Sherwin D. wrote a review Nov 2019
Phnom Penh, Cambodia17 contributions2 helpful votes
Friendly staff, nice hotel!
Loved all the staff there as they were very attentive and very helpful! Breakfast was nice and Wi-Fi was fast. Room has hair dryer, slippers and I also like their toothbrush! Hotel is pretty centrally located: close to restaurants and beach.
