Lanquan123 wrote a review Nov 2019
3 contributions
Love Minh House at the first sight
My friend and me spent two night at Minh Boutique. The hotel is amazing with unique design. How beautiful it is and so easy to go to the beach. Breakfast was yummy and good decoration. We were truly impressed by the staff because they are so attentive to us and helpful. Thanks for giving us a lovely stay. We will definitely come back to enjoy it again!
Tiennguyen wrote a review Oct 2019
Friendly hotel staff, comfortable space. Great breakfast. Will keep coming next time.
Modern architecture, with natural light and tranquility. Friendly hotel staff, good customer support. Especially the beautiful receptionist. Has a very nice pool, free breakfast. The perfect position can take 2 minutes to go to the beach and 3 minutes to go to the city center, beautiful bridges in Danang. The bedroom is clean, fully furnished. The bathroom is nice and clean. Will keep visiting when I come to Da Nang. 👍🏻
Date of stay: October 2019
Duy Tran wrote a review Aug 2019
Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam81 contributions14 helpful votes
+1
Beautiful space, friendly staffs, not comfortable rooms
What I like: - The space is extremely beautiful, designed in the style of green space brings very comfortable and relaxing time staying here. - Always play the music with a gentle harmony, you can hear in the room because the room is designed to connect the whole house, can adjust the music volume or turn off from the room very conveniently. - Rooms are spacious and clean. The balcony can see the green indoor space and the pool is very beautiful. - Staffs are extremely friendly, cute and polite. What I dislike: - Because the dining room, the kitchen and the reception counter are in the same room, it is always very smelly. - Air conditioner in the room is very old, cold mode at 20 degrees and the highest fan speed still feels hot so I have to ask for more fan. - The…
