Visit my friend Kelvin
I love this hotel and highly recommend to everyone who come to this city, Da Nang. This hotel is awesome, breakfats is delicous, room is big clean, big swimming pool and the best thing in this hotel is friendly staff especially Kelvin, my friend! He is friendly, helpful and really funny. He can speak good english and spanish. This is the first time i came to this city and had good experience. I will comeback and of coure Minh house is my first choice. Muchas gracias Kelvin. Muchos gustos y Hasta pronto en Barcelona tio
