best hotel have ever seen
Minh House is at the middle of the street, where you think there is nothing more. ... Special thanks to Kelvin the front desk who welcomed us with her big smile and came with us with his motorbike and helped us to buy some medicine and good restaurants in the area. We love this hotel so much, highly recommend and we will comeback. What a dream hotel!
